            "body": "<div>\nHi Heath,<br><br>\nI wanted to get your thoughts on the best way to incorporate an article 'summary' box on each news article on our website.<br><br>\nThe reason behind this is that I'm really trying to improve our SEO on each article but often the structure looks odd as we often launch into a bullet point summary at the top of the article which doesn't end up with the keyword(s) in etc. An example of the article structure I'm talking about is here: <a href=\"https://msra.org.au/news/shifting-goalposts-for-ms-treatment/\">https://msra.org.au/news/shifting-goalposts-for-ms-treatment/</a> <br><br>\nI'm thinking, having a box off to the right hand side within the template which could house the bullet point summary for each article could work? Do you have any thoughts on this / what the best way to display this would be? The rough idea I had is mocked up below\u2026<br><br><span><img border=\"0\" width=\"431\" height=\"511\" id=\"Picture_x0020_10\" src=\"https://d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/inline/87172/7b57e59081f66a4dabce361a98bf1a39872e6d03/1056903ddcd9ccf9d3c9181392c51c9860c56ff2/image010.png\" alt=\"https://d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/inline/87172/7b57e59081f66a4dabce361a98bf1a39872e6d03/1056903ddcd9ccf9d3c9181392c51c9860c56ff2/image010.png\" /></span><br><br>\nThanks<br><br>\nLizzy <br><br><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"102\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:76.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<a href=\"http://www.msra.org.au/\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;text-decoration:none;\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"88\" height=\"96\" id=\"Picture_x0020_1\" src=\"https://d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/inline/87172/ccfe31f4de686d3deb19a76d03159d8364f9118f/1aa89b234de13a2f207cd3ecef4d507193253aa0/image001.jpg\" alt=\"Latest MSRA_logo trimmed\" /></span></a><span style=\"color:#000;\"></span><br></td>\n<td width=\"443\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:332.6pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">Lizzy Morton</span></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">Marketing and Communications</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">Coordinator</span><br><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">MS Research Australia</span><br><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">02 8413 791</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1F497D;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#F00;\">\u2022</span> <span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">1300 356 467</span><br><span><a href=\"mailto:emorton@msra.org.au\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#0563C1;\">emorton@msra.org.au</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#F00;\">\u2022</span> <span><a href=\"http://www.msra.org.au/\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#0563C1;\">www.msra.org.au</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\"></span><br><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">Level 19 Northpoint</span> <span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#F00;\">\u2022</span> <span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">100 Miller Street</span> <span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#F00;\">\u2022</span> <span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000;\">North Sydney NSW 2060</span><br></td>\n</tr></tbody></table><span style=\"color:#000;\"></span><p></p><br><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MSResearchAustralia\"><span style=\"color:#000;text-decoration:none;\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" id=\"Pi